      "num": "04 · the takeaway",
      "heading": "A queue is a promise to finish later",
      "blocks": [
        {
          "type": "prose",
          "html": "<p class=\"body\">Use queues when later is acceptable, then make later observable enough that nobody has to guess.</p>"
